        {
          "doc": "Maps `arg_index \\xe2\\x86\\x92 index of a prior instruction whose return value\\nshould replace that arg slot at runtime`. Empty map = no substitutions.\\n\\nAUTH NOTE: arg substitution is auth-safe under source-account auth\\n(the standard Freighter / EOA flow). For sponsored or address-credentials\\nauth flows where the auth entry is bound to specific args, callers MUST\\nkeep `arg_refs` empty and pass concrete values \\xe2\\x80\\x94 runtime drift will\\notherwise mismatch the signed auth entry and the tx will revert.",
